      "text": [
        " : قُلْتُ لَهُ اَلرَّجُلُ يُقِرُّ لِوَارِثٍ بِدَيْنٍ عَلَيْهِ فَقَالَ \"يَجُوزُ إِذَا كَانَ مَلِيّاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5541 - Hammad narrated from Al-Halabi from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n'I asked Imam (as) about a man who acknowledges a debt to one of his heirs.'\nImam (as) said: \"It is permissible if he is solvent (financially capable).\""
        ]
      }
